usermin: webmin (web-based interface for user needs)
usermin:
usermin: Usermin is a web-based interface for webmail, password changing, mail
usermin: filters, fetchmail and much more. It is designed for use by regular
usermin: non-root users on a Unix system, and limits them to tasks that they
usermin: would be able to perform if logged in via SSH or at the console.
